  "text": "The problem considered is defined hereunder. This problem is a generalization of the one in [CITATION_1] . The difference is that we do not only seek a filter respecting a given level ||G|| ∞ < γ but we rather wish to minimize this level. This objective is more meaningful and also more practical for the user who does not need to choose an arbitrary level γ beforehand. Note that considering the expression of A f , since Σ is stable we have that the filtering error system Σ e is stable iff the filterΣ is stable.",
